reviewText: Such inspiration, ingenuity, and the strong will of some of America's greatest soldiers.
Excellent series with in-depth first person interviews. Highly Recommended!!!!!

by fare a rare look inside the warrior life stlye of the green berets.. could have had more recent events and missions comparing the past to present in a little more depth, but all in all Great!!  If you Love spec ops history or are considering joining the military spec ops community heres a great look to help you decision.  Should be in every military buffs video library!
